message.turtleblockacademy.registered: You are now registered as a student of Turtle Block Academy
tooltip.turtleblockacademy.easter_egg_it:
In China, children celebrate the spring equinox by trying to balance their decorated eggs on their ends.
Success is believed to bring good luck for the year.
Provides Comfort effect for a brief time.
tooltip.turtleblockacademy.pickled_item_:
Did you know that vinegar helps fabrics hold on to natural pigments longer?
Be careful not to spill your pickled beets onto your clothes!
Did you know that the United States has a national pickle day on November 14th?

Unpasteurized fermented foods are probiotic and when stored well,
they promote good gut bacterial health.
To reflect this, these pickles will remove one negative effect when consumed.
